........Problem........

Create a BMI assessment function called ‘checkHealth()’ that takes the weight and
height of an individual as its parameters and returns whether the individual is
‘underweight’, ‘normal’, ‘overweight’ or ‘obese’.

........Soution........

FUNCTION checkHealth(weight, height):
	
	VAR bmi
	bmi = weight / (height * height)
    
	IF bmi <18.5 DO:
		
		PRINT "underweight"
		
	ELSE IF bmi >= 18.5 AND bmi <= 24.9 DO:
	
		PRINT "Normal"
		
	ELSE IF bmi >=25 AND bmi <= 29.9 DO:
	
		PRINT "Overweight"
		
	ELSE DO:
	
		PRINT "Obese"
	
	ENDIF


ENDFUNCTION
